{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "舞台上的怪物人偶第1话 演员的登场",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "加斯特和莱姬希来到了镇上的剧院。\\n委托加斯特进行熏香治疗的剧作家梅洛\\n一见到莱姬希就决定让她出演自己剧中\\n的主角。莱姬希则从剧本中感受到了\\n“心”的存在，于是同意出演主角。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "不～给～糖……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "就～捣～蛋！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "马上就到恶作剧的季节了！\\n大家也来一起快乐吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希&加斯特",
            "context": "不要。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "唔！？什么嘛，\\n你们俩也太不配合了吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "随你怎么说。\\n我今天收到了熏香治疗的委托，\\n没工夫陪你闹。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "委托……我和你一起去。\\n出门的话就不会被卢卡捉弄了。\\n——莱姬希，也不用这么躲着他吧……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "啧……那还真是不好意思啊。\\n我只是……一心希望你们也能\\n好好享受节日而已……呜呜。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "唉……别哭了，卢卡。\\n想让别人也享受其中的话，\\n就要稍微动动脑筋……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "骗你的！我没哭！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希&加斯特",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "哇哈哈！我是不是演得很逼真？\\n这是我从马萝拉那儿学的绝招！\\n说是叫“眼泪攻势”！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03",
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希&加斯特",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "你给我……适可而止！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "这里就是委托人指定的地点了……\\n真是人山人海啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "予以赞同。我还是第一次来\\n人群如此密集的地方。\\n——这是什么地方啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "是市民剧场。\\n看歌舞和戏剧的地方。\\n后门在……那边吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "那么委托人在……嗯？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女演员",
            "context": "我受够了！不演了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "演员",
            "context": "我也是。虽说一路以来我们\\n克服了很多问题，\\n但这次怕是无法奉陪了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "等、等等！你们要是现在\\n辞演的话……唔！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120091_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "剧场老板",
            "context": "梅洛，这还是太乱来了……\\n我们就放弃这场戏，\\n准备下一场如何？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "不行！无论是剧本还是舞台布景，\\n我都会争取赶上万圣节的。\\n演员也……只要再找就好！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120091_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "剧场老板",
            "context": "可是……\\n现在离演出只剩不到一个月了啊！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "这……\\n没问题的……我会想办法！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120091_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "剧场老板",
            "context": "唉……好吧。不过要是\\n找不到演员的话就老老实实放弃，\\n到时我会着手准备下一场戏的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "可恶！我要赶紧……想想办法……\\n咳、咳咳！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "打扰一下，\\n请问你就是梅洛吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "嗯？你是？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "我叫加斯特。是你写信给我说\\n想要缓解病症的熏香的吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "你就是加斯特……还特地赶来的吗。\\n多谢……咳咳！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "看来需要治疗的\\n就是你本人了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "嗯。我是个剧作家……\\n为了舞台剧创作太过劳累，\\n结果犯了老毛病。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "但我没时间去医院。\\n我无论如何都想要完成这个剧本，\\n任何事都不能阻拦我……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "（看来是有什么隐情啊。\\n不过……也不好开口去问。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "我明白了。\\n我的同伴已经去问有没有空房间了，\\n等有了消息就赶快开始治疗吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "加斯特，我借到了一个适合治疗的\\n小休息室，可以去那边……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "唔！你……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "嗯？怎么了，梅洛？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "你、你这是人偶装扮吗！？\\n这妆是怎么化出来的？\\n这球形关节简直可以以假乱真……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "嗯？你是谁？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "哇！关节还可以活动！\\n难道你是真的人偶！？\\n唔……咳、咳咳！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "啊……她的事情我之后再跟你解释。\\n现在先来治疗吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "呼……我没事了。\\n竟然能让呼吸变得这么畅快，\\n你的熏香真厉害啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "而且，要说厉害……\\n你叫莱姬希对吧，你也很厉害呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "你就是古代文明的文献中\\n记载的战斗人偶……对吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "予以部分肯定。严格来说，\\n我不是诞生于古代的战斗人偶。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "这样啊……\\n不过没想到这世上竟然还存在\\n如此工艺精巧的人偶……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "那个……莱姬希。\\n你能答应我一个请求吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "请求……什么请求？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "就是……\\n求你了！\\n能在我的舞台剧中扮演主角吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "话剧？\\n——诶……诶诶！？莱姬希演主角？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "梅洛，你突然说什么呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "其实……你看看这个。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——这是什么？\\n——是手写稿。有好多啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "是剧本啊……好像还没写完。\\n是你现在在写的作品？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "没错。这是将要在\\n万圣节上演的新剧目——\\n《向爱而生的怪物》。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "故事的世界背景与现实不同，\\n是由“电”与“机械”构成的新世界……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "故事的主角则是\\n人造的怪物……人偶。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——人偶……\\n——和我们一样！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "原来如此。由人偶来演人偶，\\n演出的确会显得更真实呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "是啊。而且这部话剧的\\n准备工作困难重重，\\n进展不太乐观。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "主演也都辞演了。\\n所以如果你愿意出演的话，\\n这场戏就还有机会。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "我会为你量身撰写台词，\\n你也不需要刻意表演，怎么样？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "就算你这么说……\\n莱姬希，你认为呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——……\\n梅洛，你是怎么研发制造出\\n“这个”的？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "研发制造？没那么夸张……\\n作家所做的，无非就是\\n用纸和笔将想象化为文字罢了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "无法理解。感情……“心”\\n不可能那么容易就能创造出来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "诶？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0069",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "为了能够辨别善恶，\\n战斗人偶指挥官机体上所搭载的\\n自我系统“心”能够输出带有情感的信息。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0070",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "将这种模拟人类感情的信息\\n与己方同步，便可以对复杂的\\n状况进行判断和反馈。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0071",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "据我观察，“这个”也有同样的性质。\\n输出情感并与他人同步，\\n也就是说这里边也包含“心”，不是吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0072",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "那个……我听不太懂……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0073",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——唔……\\n我想莱姬希应该想说这个剧本\\n很“有趣”吧……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0074",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——有趣？与无机物情感同步\\n就是对艺术感到有趣吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0075",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——也、也许是吧……比如有个词\\n叫“同理心”，对文学艺术而言，\\n情感同步应该也很重要吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0076",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——予以部分理解。但是，\\n梅洛说这个还没写完。也就是说……\\n情感同步还并不完整……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0077",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "那个……如果我演主角，\\n你就能让我看到故事的后续吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0078",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "诶？嗯，当然！\\n只要你肯演，这部剧离完成\\n就能更近一步。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0079",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "现在已经没有可以研发“心”的人了……\\n我们的系统也仍存在诸多未解之谜。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0080",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "通过协助你创作剧本，\\n也许能弄明白“心”的原理。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0081",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "所以，\\n我原意来演这个剧本的主角。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0082",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "真、真的吗？太谢谢你了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0083",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "喂……剧本里可不会有什么\\n解析战斗人偶系统的线索哦？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0084",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——啊哈哈……不过，\\n也算助人为乐了……是吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0085",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "我穿上演出服装试了试。\\n可爱吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0086",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "啊，嗯……\\n倒是挺可爱的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0087",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "没错！真的很适合你呢，莱姬希。\\n这下话剧也就有希望了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0088",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "是吗，我想帮更多忙。\\n还有什么需要我做的？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0089",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "嗯……其他演员就由我负责来找，\\n剩下就是舞台布景了。\\n其实主要的布景还没搭完。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0090",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "舞台布景吗……\\n真是前途堪忧啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0091",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "盯——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0092",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "怎么了，莱姬希？\\n你那是什么眼神……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0093",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "你也会每天来这里给梅洛治疗，\\n可以帮忙。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0094",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "等等。我的工作是治疗病人，\\n和舞台剧没关系吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0095",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "盯——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0096",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "唔。唉……好吧。\\n我会筹措舞台要用的材料，\\n帮忙搭布景的，这总行了吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0097",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "予以肯定。——啊、啊哈哈……\\n不好意思，莱姬希太任性了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0098",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110318_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加斯特",
            "context": "没事。完成以后\\n梅洛也就不用再如此劳累了。\\n我的治疗也能快点结束。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0099",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅洛",
            "context": "多谢二位。\\n为了演出成功……就麻烦你们了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20837_01_0100",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}